prompts.name: Schrödinger's Amusement Park
prompts.prompt: 144p, vhs filter, poor quality, low resolution, image noise, hot pixels, old photo, theme park where all rides exist in multiple states simultaneously, roller coasters with quantum tunneling, ferris wheel rotating in impossible directions, carousel horses phasing in and out of reality, cotton candy made of probability clouds, park visitors existing and not existing, entrance gates leading to multiple parallel parks
prompts.negative_prompt: good quality, 4k, high definition, classical physics, single state of being, normal theme park rides, consistent reality
prompts.description: An entertainment venue where the fundamental uncertainties of quantum mechanics are scaled up to the macroscopic world, offering thrills that defy not just gravity, but reality itself.

prompts.name: Cybernetic Dreamscape
prompts.prompt: 8K, neon lights, chrome surfaces, digital dreamscape, impossible architecture, bioluminescent flora, levitating walkways, holographic projections, park visitors with cybernetic implants, rides that merge physical reality with the digital world
prompts.negative_prompt: blurry, low resolution, nature elements, realistic physics, theme park limitations, single reality
prompts.description: A futuristic amusement park where the lines between human and machine blur, offering experiences that redefine the boundaries of perception.

prompts.name: Underwater Wonderland
prompts.prompt: bioluminescent lighting, deep sea, coral reefs, schools of exotic fish, transparent tunnels, weightless environment, giant kelp forests, aquatic creatures as rides, park visitors breathe underwater, sunken ruins

prompts.name: Threshold Train Station
prompts.prompt: sepia tone, hand drawn lines, antique paper texture, run down train station at twilight, trains arriving from various timelines, ticket booth serving tickets for alternate realities, passengers merging between dimensions, flickering lights indicating temporal instability
